Title: Pharaoh
Writer: Boleslaw Prus (novel), Tadeusz Konwicki (screenplay), Jerzy Kawalerowicz (screenplay)
Actors: Jerzy Zelnik, Wieslawa Mazurkiewicz, Barbara Brylska, Krystyna Mikolajewska
Plot: Young Pharaoh Ramses XIII clashes with Egypt's clergy over influence on the affairs of the state and its coffers.
